{"tid":345003,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[雲加又中] 雲格︰2億鎊身價球員好快出現","createTime":"2017-08-02T16:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T02:19:55.000Z","uid":32938,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c3ee4fd488f98cea7f14171a18ca8af623163a6","tid":345003,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:42:26.000Z","msg":"2016年8月13日 上午06:07:14<br />\n眼見保羅普巴天價回歸曼聯，阿仙奴領隊雲格預期，2億英鎊轉會費的交易很快便出現，但他相信阿仙奴在這個金錢世界的球壇仍然具競爭力。<br />\n<br />\n向來慳檢的兵工廠，今季暫時只有以3400萬英鎊買入瑞士中場格列沙加的貴價收購，但與普巴8930萬鎊的身價相比實在差天共地，雲格說︰「很快便有1.5億或2億鎊轉會費的交易出現，雖然我早已說過這需耍制止，但當金錢不斷湧入時情況便是這樣。有趣的是當不少本土企業苦苦經營時，一些國際品牌像facebook、Google和足球等便有無窮無盡的收入。」<br />\n<br />\n不過雲格重申，他仍然相信金錢不一定是錦標保證︰「曼聯與皇馬是全球最有錢球會，財力上沒有其他球隊可與他們比拼，但在球場上卻沒有分別，金錢競逐不一定反映在聯賽榜上，李斯特城便是一個好例子。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=q7VntjqcN0D1Vxs6osFulDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=29e8bb70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"2352fa448c96086b99b92bb41089ca609ed29939","tid":345003,"uid":13088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"金錢競逐不一定反映在聯賽榜上，李斯特城便是一個好例子。<br />\n<br />\nCloud add<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3050480e489b533e5c1a9e8ce94d98f09d5d8736","tid":345003,"uid":3832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T18:59:10.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0b44f069756150c506380cbee1088dae0b6d89","tid":345003,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T23:00:14.000Z","msg":"又然 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff46dbafff467784142fea45993edbe41b58827","tid":345003,"uid":84228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T00:11:19.000Z","